questions.quote: I know, just quick-quick question, quick question. Which one was Deep Impact and which one was Armageddon?
Yeah, I-I don't, I can't get away with stuff like that. I-I-It sounded sexy in my head, so I...
So.. let me get this straight. So my two friends die, I get Emma. Then my wife dies, then Emma the one tiny ray of hope left in my life gets taken away from me?
Okay, okay, I'm sure that Rachel came home early and picked up Emma. You go look across the hall, and I'll call her cell.
Becasue it reminded you of the way our forefathers used to bitch at each other?
I didn't! Even when I found out...umm, all right, well let's just say I found something out something about someone and let's just say she's gonna keep it.
Oh, you want something serious. Y'know what you should do, you should get her one of those um, barium enemas. Those are dead serious.
Yeah, well he'd prefer water colors, but y'know, he has easy access to a lot of charcoal.
Well maybe he was just nervous, y'know you can be very intimidating. And besides I've met your pastry chef and she can stand to be taken down a peg or two.
Well, I guess there's nothing left for us to do but-but kiss.
